creator: Muhammad Faris
descriptionHtml:
FNTrack provides a most up to date information such as daily Item Shop, In Game News, search for player statistics and more. FNTrack is also customizable such as the ability to switch between Light & Dark mode with themes based on some rarities colors. All these features are completely free with no in app purchase or ads!

**Quick Information**

Home page that contains quick information such as In Game News, daily bundle items and even the current season map. Sometimes losing a game can be demotivated right? Don’t worry, on the home page I have included random generated motivational quotes to motivate you to keep grinding the game and maybe become a Pro?

**Language Support**

Information such as In Game News, Shop, Cosmetic Details and Achievements, supports up to 11 different languages. Default is set to English, but you can change it within the Settings page.

**Achievements**

View all available achievements within the app so you can focus on the game and not get distracted by finding the achievements you’re looking for in the game menu.

**Item Shop**

Beautiful card design to showcase the current game item shop as soon as its updated so you can decide which cosmetics you would like to purchase anywhere without opening the game.

**Cosmetic Details**

Select on any items in the item shop page to view a detailed information of rarity, price in item shop, set, description, added on, shop history and more. You could also search for a cosmetics name and view those details too.

**Player Statistics**

Search for any player to view their statistics with every input for example Keyboard & Mouse, Controller or Touch. Every input will include statistics such as solo, duos, squads.

**App Customisation**

Features a customisable app such as ability to switch between Light or Dark Mode. It even has 6 themes for you to choose from that is based on some of the rarities in game. So customize the app to your liking!

-- Disclaimer--

FNTrack is an unofficial app that is not affiliated, associated or endorsed by Epic Games. The official Epic Games website can be found at epicgames.com.

-- Get in Touch --

If you have any questions, suggestions or feedback, please get in touch. I have a lot of features planned for future updates so stay tuned for that. FNTrack was created by an incredibly small team of one and I’d love to hear your thoughts. I’m available through Twitter @muhd_faris03 or email me at support@farisfaisal.com or even through the in-app feedback.

title: FNTrack - Tracker for FN

creator: Muhammad Faris
descriptionHtml:
FNTrack provides the most up to date information such as daily item shop, In Game News, Players Statistics and more! FNTrack is highly customisable from the background theme to the 6 beautiful accent colours to match your style. Everything in FNTrack is completely free with no ads!

**Quick Information**
Dashboard page that contains quick information such as in-game news, current shop section, countdown for the next season and more! If you feel the Dashboard is cluttered with many information you could also customise in settings on which information you want to see only!

**Language Support**
Information such as Shop Sections, Item Shop, In Game News, Challenges and more, supports up to 11 different languages which you can change in Settings!

**Challenges**
View all available challenges or filter them to show only weekly challenges so you won’t distract yourself to look these up in game!

**Item Shop**
Beautiful card design item shop which is grouped by their sections!

**Quiz**
Test your knowledge with some of the categories such as BR Map, Cosmetics and more. More categories coming soon!

**Customisation**
FNTrack is highly customisable by providing you the the ability to switch between light or dark mode, changing the accent theme, hiding the tabs title, more page layout and many more.

**More**
Stay motivated with Motivational Quotes that can be found on the Dashboard page. Player Settings provides you information with some of the most popular players game settings, key binds, hardware setups and more. There are many features available in FNTrack so download today and explore them! FNTrack is features packed so you will have everything you need all in one app.

—Disclaimer—
FNTrack is an unofficial Fortnite app that is not affiliated, associated, or endorsed by Epic Games. The official Epic Games website can be found at epicgames.com.

—Contact—
If you have any questions, suggestions, or feedback please get in touch with me. You could also follow me on twitter @FNTrackApp to stay updated with the latest features and changes. FNTrack was created by an incredibly small team of one and I’d love to hear your thoughts. I’m also available through twitter @faris_develop @FNTrackApp or email me at faris.developments@gmail.com

title: FNTrack - FN Companion

creator: Muhammad Faris
descriptionHtml:
FNTrack is a companion app you need for FN that provides the most up to date information such as daily item shop, blog and competitive news, player statistics, challenges and more. There’re no ads too!

Push Notifications
When you’re logged into FNTrack, you will be able to receive Push Notifications for your wish lists cosmetics, weekly challenges, tournaments and more.

Informative
View any information related to FN whether it's Arena, Challenges, Crew Packs, Game Status, Item Shop, Tournaments, Weapons Statistics and so much more all in one single app.

Customisation
FNTrack is super customisable because you can switch between Light or Dark mode, Accent themes, Time Format and much more.

Item Shop
Registered FNTrack users will be able to vote the item shop daily. Item Shop is also updated while you’re viewing the page without the need to refresh the information.

News
You can view any FN news in FNTrack whether its Blog Post, Competitive News or In Game news.

Cosmetics Combinations
You can now create your own skin combinations along with pickaxe, glider, and back bling.

Tournament
View all upcoming tournaments in a unified view so you will be able to see which tournaments is happening when and how long exactly. Besides that, select any tournaments to view more in dept details such as every session, scorings, leader board and more.

More
Player Settings provides you information with some of the most popular players game settings, key binds, hardware setups and more. Randomiser allows you to randomise cosmetics, POI and more so you can challenge yourself! There are many features available in FNTrack so download today and explore them! FNTrack is features packed so you will have everything you need all in one app.

—Disclaimer—
FNTrack is an unofficial FN app that is not affiliated, associated, or endorsed by Epic Games. The official Epic Games website can be found at epicgames.com.

—Contact—
If you have any questions, suggestions, or feedback please get in touch with me. You could also follow me on twitter @FNTrackApp to stay updated with the latest features and changes. FNTrack was created by an incredibly small team of one and I’d love to hear your thoughts. I’m also available through twitter @FNTrackApp or email me at faris.developments@gmail.com

When you’re logged into FNTrack, you will be able to receive Push Notifications for your wish lists cosmetics, weekly challenges, tournaments and more.

Informative
View any information related to FN whether it's Arena, Challenges, Crew Packs, Game Status, Item Shop, Tournaments, Weapons Statistics and so much more all in one single app.

Customisation
FNTrack is super customisable because you can switch between Light or Dark mode, Accent themes, Time Format and much more.

Item Shop
Registered FNTrack users will be able to vote the item shop daily. Item Shop is also updated while you’re viewing the page without the need to refresh the information.

News
You can view any FN news in FNTrack whether its Blog Post, Competitive News or In Game news.

Cosmetics Combinations
You can now create your own skin combinations along with pickaxe, glider, and back bling.

Tournament
View all upcoming tournaments in a unified view so you will be able to see which tournaments is happening when and how long exactly. Besides that, select any tournaments to view more in dept details such as every session, scorings, leader board and more.

More
Player Settings provides you information with some of the most popular players game settings, key binds, hardware setups and more. Randomiser allows you to randomise cosmetics, POI and more so you can challenge yourself! There are many features available in FNTrack so download today and explore them! FNTrack is features packed so you will have everything you need all in one app.

—Disclaimer—
FNTrack is an unofficial FN app that is not affiliated, associated, or endorsed by Epic Games. The official Epic Games website can be found at epicgames.com.

—Contact—
If you have any questions, suggestions, or feedback please get in touch with me. You could also follow me on twitter @FNTrackApp to stay updated with the latest features and changes. FNTrack was created by an incredibly small team of one and I’d love to hear your thoughts. I’m also available through twitter @FNTrackApp or email me at faris.developments@gmail.com
